'''Francisco Manso''' (yavutse 28 Ugushyingo 1949), ni producer akaba n'umukinnyi wa filimi wo muri portigali. <ref>https://letterboxd.com/director/francisco-manso/</ref> Azwi cyane nk'umuyobozi wa firime zizwi cyane,''Napomuceno's Will'', ''[[:en:The_Consul_of_Bordeaux|The Consul of Bordeaux]]'' and ''O Nosso Cônsul em Havana'' <ref>http://www.cinept.ubi.pt/pt/filme/10831/O+Nosso+C%C3%B4nsul+em+Havana</ref>.<ref>https://spiamedia.com/the-consul-of-bordeaux-2/</ref>

== Umwuga ==
Yarangije amategeko muri kaminuza ya Lisbonne . Mu 1976, yarangije muri firime muri Centro de Arte e Comunicação Visual (Ar.Co) maze, mu 1979 kugeza 1980, arangiza amasomo y’ubuhanga bw’amajwi maze aba umuyobozi wungirije muri televiziyo rusange Rádio e Televisão de Portugal (RTP). <ref>http://euffto.com/index.php/festival-archives/item/francisco-manso</ref><ref>https://www.ipea.gov.br/desafios/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=2967:catid=28&Itemid=23</ref>

Mu 1978, yimukiye muri sinema nk'umuyobozi wungirije wa mbere wa filime ''O Meu Nome É'', iyobowe na Fernando Matos Silva. Ibyo byakurikiwe na ''O Príncipe com Orelhas de Burro'', iyobowe na António de Macedo, mu 1979. Mu 1980, yimukiye muri [[Gineya-Biso|Gineya Bissau]] akora kuri filime ''Acto dos Feitos da Guiné'' iyobowe na Matos Silva. Mu mwaka wakurikiyeho, yasubiye muri Porutugali maze akora kuri filime ''Guerra no Mirandum ya'' Matos Silva yo mu 1981.<ref>https://www.3continents.com/fr/film/acto-dos-feitos-da-guine/</ref><ref>https://cinemaportuguesmemoriale.pt/Filmes/id/385/t/o-principe-com-orelhas-de-burro/</ref>
[[Dosiye:The_film_Director,_Francisco_Manso_along_with_the_actor_Vitor_Norte,_the_producer,_Jose_Mazeda_and_the_composer_Henri_Seroka_addressing_a_press_conference_during_the_42nd_International_Film_Festival_of_India_(IFFI-2011).jpg|right|thumb| Umuyobozi wa firime, Francisco Manso (uwa kabiri uhereye ibumoso) hamwe n'umukinnyi Vitor Norte, producer, Jose Mazeda, hamwe nuwahimbye Henri Seroka ubwo yaganiraga n’abanyamakuru mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya sinema mpuzamahanga rya 42 (IFFI-2011)]]
Nyuma yo gukora nk'umufasha imyaka myinshi, umurimo wa mbere wa Manso wo kuyobora ni 1983 hamwe na filimi ya televiziyo ''A Epopeia dos Bacalhaus'' . Yahinduye kandi filime ye ya mbere yerekanwe kuri tereviziyo, ''Terra Nova, Mar Velho'', muri uwo mwaka. Iyo filime imaze gutsinda, yakomeje kuyobora filime na documentaire nka, ''A Aposta'' (1987), ''Na Mão de Deus'' (1989), ''Nostalgia'' (1994) na ''O Espírito da Cor'' (1994). <ref name="caboverde">http://www.caboverde-info.com/ger/Identitaet/Persoenlichkeiten/Francisco-Manso</ref><ref>https://africanfilmny.org/directors/francisco-manso/</ref><ref>https://www.estantevirtual.com.br/livros/francisco-manso-e-oscar-cruz/a-epopeia-dos-bacalhaus</ref>

Mu 1997, Manso yakoze filime ye ya mbere yerekana sinema, ''O Testamento do Senhor Napomuceno'', ashingiye ku gitabo cyitwa ''The Will Will and Testament of Senhor da Silva Araújo'' cyanditswe na Germano Almeida kirwa cya [[Kapu Veri|Cape Verde]] . Filime yatanzwe ku rwego mpuzamahanga kandi yerekanwe mu minsi mikuru ya firime, ihabwa ibihembo byinshi harimo bitatu mu iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Gramado . Mu 2000, yakoze TV mini-serie ''Almeida Garrett'' . Inyandiko ye, ''Memórias de um rio - Avieiros, os nómadas do Tejo'' mu 2004, yahawe igihembo cyihariye cya Lusophony mu iserukiramuco rya Filime rya 10 ry’ibidukikije - Cine Eco 2004. <ref>https://www.publico.pt/2019/01/17/culturaipsilon/critica/caso-anulado-falta-provas-1857965</ref><ref>https://www.allmovie.com/artist/francisco-manso-p242025</ref>

Muri filime yakurikiyeho yakoresheje cyane cyane amateka, nka firime ''O Último Condenado à Morte'' ya 2008, yabayeho mugihe cya Revolution Liberal muri Portugal muri 1821/22. Mu mwaka wa 2011, yakoze filime ''O Cônsul de Bordéus'' yari ishingiye ku buzima bwa Aristides de Sousa Mendes ndetse n’ibikorwa yakoreye ikiremwamuntu mu gihe cyo gutoteza Abayahudi. <ref>https://www.publico.pt/2011/09/13/culturaipsilon/noticia/quoto-consul-de-bordeusquot-esgotou-cinemateca-de-televive-293255</ref><ref>https://ukjewishfilm.org/film/the-consul-of-bordeaux/</ref>

